<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Gebhard Stör von Störnstein</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Wölflein Schultheiß, Diener der Stadt, wegen Herausgabe der acht bei Kirchenthumbach geraubten Pferde des Hans Scheffel, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_385" id="192r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_385_r1l18"><expan>Gebharte<ex>n</ex></expan> Stör </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_385_r1l19"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Gebhart vns hat furgelegt Hans Scheffell vnſer <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l20">vvie daʒ Jr vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> helffer Jm viij pferde bey Tumpach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l21"><expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir cʒu ew den wölfell <expan>Schulth<ex>eiſʒ</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l22"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıener mit ew dauon ʒureden / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıener <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> ʒu diſem mal an euch werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_385_r1l24">vvegen / daʒ Jr Jm des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_385" id="192r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Gebharte<ex>n</ex></expan> Stör </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Gebhart, uns hat
                                                furgelegt Hans Scheffell, unser
                                                  <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz ir und
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> helffer im viii pferde
                                                bey Tumpach <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt,
                                                  <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czu ew den
                                                Wölfell <expan>Schulth<ex>eisz</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit ew
                                                davon zureden, und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                                                waz der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener
                                                  <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> zu disem mal an
                                                euch werb von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen,
                                                daz ir im des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
